name: RBC U.S. Dividend Covered Call ETF
longDescription: The investment objective of the ETF is to provide unitholders with exposure to the performance of a diversified portfolio of high quality US equity securities that are expected to provide regular income from dividends and have the potential for long term capital growth. The ETF invests primarily in an actively managed portfolio of US companies with above-average dividend yield or with good prospects of paying or growing their dividends. Depending on market volatility and other factors, the ETF will write covered call options on some of these securities.
